# Ignore all PDF files in any directory
*.pdf

# This will ignore PDFs in:
# - Root directory: file.pdf
# - Any subdirectory: folder/file.pdf
# - Nested directories: folder/subfolder/file.pdf
# - Files with any name: document.pdf, report.pdf, etc.

# If you ever need to force-add a specific PDF despite this rule, you can use:
# git add -f path/to/specific.pdf
